    <div class="boutique-intro__container">
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-lg boutique-intro__heading">A Quinceañera Partner, Not Just a Dress Shop</h2>
      
      <p class="boutique-intro__text">
        Your quinceañera is a milestone moment—a celebration of family, culture, and the beautiful young woman you're becoming. At Vero's, we understand the significance of XV. It's not about filling a closet; it's about honoring tradition while expressing your unique style. Our team of XV specialists has spent years perfecting the art of quinceañera styling—from gown selection to court coordination.
      </p>

      <p class="boutique-intro__text">
        We celebrate diverse cultural expressions of XV. Whether your celebration follows tradition or creates something entirely new, we're here to support your vision. Our bilingual team understands the importance of family involvement. We welcome mothers, grandmothers, and court members to fittings. We guide court aesthetic decisions. We listen to your cultural preferences, timeline needs, and dream vision.
      </p>

      <div class="button-row">
        <a href="/book-an-appointment/" class="button button--primary">Schedule Your 90-Minute XV Fitting</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

